title: TUXEDO Linux Gaming Laptops Powered by AMD Ryzen 7000 Series CPUs Are Back
description:
TUXEDO Computers announces the Gen5 TUXEDO Polaris 15 and TUXEDO Stellaris 16 Linux gaming laptops with AMD Ryzen 7000 Series CPUs, high-end NVIDIA graphics, and up to 96 GB DDR5 RAM.
